></div></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Fournir du contexte</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Les prestataires voient une image plus riche lorsque les patients choisissent de partager.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0"><div class="p-3 bg-orange-startup/20 rounded-full"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-users h-6 w-6 text-orange-startup" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><path d="M16 3.128a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.744"></path><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle></svg></div></div><div><h3 class="font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">Encourager l&#x27;engagement</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Les patients deviennent des participants actifs dans leurs soins.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-white"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-blue-light/20 text-blue-vibrant px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-blue-vibrant/30">Documentation Centrée Patient</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Un Espace Privé pour les Notes de Santé</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Les patients peuvent écrire librement dans leurs propres mots — notes courtes ou réflexions plus longues — sachant qu&#x27;ils contrôlent ce qui est partagé.</p></div><div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8"><div class="space-y-4 "><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-smartphone h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><path d="M12 18h.01"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Accessible à tout moment sur web ou mobile</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Disponible via la connexion au portail patient existant</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4 "><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-square-pen h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-7"></path><path d="M18.375 2.625a1 1 0 0 1 3 3l-9.013 9.014a2 2 0 0 1-.853.505l-2.873.84a.5.5 0 0 1-.62-.62l.84-2.873a2 2 0 0 1 .506-.852z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Format d&#x27;entrée flexible, des notes rapides aux histoires plus longues</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Écrivez dans vos propres mots et votre style</p></div></div></div><div class="space-y-4 md:col-span-2"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-shield h-6 w-6 text-blue-vibrant flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z"></path></svg><div><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-1">Confidentialité d&#x27;abord : les entrées restent privées sauf si partagées</h3><p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Vous contrôlez quelles informations partager et quand</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="lg:w-full"><div class="relative"><img alt="Patient utilisant un journal santé numérique sur appareil mobile" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_journal%2Fpatient_centered_documentation.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_journal%2Fpatient_centered_documentation.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_journal%2Fpatient_centered_documentation.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="lg:w-full lg:order-1"><div class="relative"><img alt="Patient partageant sélectivement des entrées de journal santé avec le prestataire" loading="lazy" width="600" height="400" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover aspect-4/3" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_journal%2Fselective-sharing-with-providers.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_journal%2Fselective-sharing-with-providers.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fhealth_journal%2Fselective-sharing-with-providers.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-green-success/20 text-green-success px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-green-success/30">Partage Contrôlé par le Patient</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Partage Sélectif avec les Prestataires</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">